/210/s203/f"},"text":"section 203(f) of Pub. L. 107–210","children":[],"tail":", set out as a Construction note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s35"},"text":"section 35 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
